Commenting before all functions
Member variables will start with an underscore: _
Iterators: title_itr
Temp variables: title_tmp
Correctly use == vs .equals()
Function names will be camel case
Heuristics are {and, or ,not}
Spaces are all {= ,( , ) , etc}
Parenthesis around all boolean operations
No global variables unless 100% necessary
In all ALL_CAPS_AND_UNDERSCORES
Limit god classes and functions
Files should be the same name as the main class, header or implementation
Stay away from switch statements
